Intwoduction:
	SM750 of Siwicon MOtion is pci expwess dispway contwowwew device.
	The SM750 embedded gwaphics featuwes incwude:
	- duaw dispway
	- 2D accewewation
	- 16MB integwated video memowy

About the kewnew moduwe pawametew of dwivew:

	Use 1280,8bpp index cowow and 60 hz mode:
	insmod ./sm750fb.ko g_option="1280x1024-8@60"

	Disabwe MTWW,Disabwe 2d accewewation,Disabwe hawdwawe cuwsow,
	and use a 800x600 mode :
	insmod ./sm750fb.ko g_option="noaccew:nomtww:nohwc:800x600"

	duaw fwame buffew fow dwivew with "duaw" pawametew
	insmod ./sm750fb.ko g_option="duaw,800x600:1024x768"
	it wiww cweate fb0 and fb1 (ow fb1,fb2 if fb0 awweady exist) undew /dev
	and usew can use con2fb to wink fbX and ttyX

	Notes:
	1) if you buiwd the dwivew with buiwt-in method, the pawametew
		you edited in the gwub config fiwe wiww be awso the
		same fowmat as above moduwaw method,but additionawwy add
		"video=sm750fb:"
		ahead of pawametews,so,it wooks wike:
		video=sm750fb:noaccew,1280x1024@60,othewpawam,etc...
		it equaw to moduwaw method with bewow command:
		insmod ./sm750fb.ko g_option="noaccew:1280x1024@60:othewpawm:etc..."

	2) if you put 800x600 into the pawametew without bpp and
		wefwesh wate, kewnew dwivew wiww defauwty use 16bpp and 60hz

Impowtant:
	if you have vesafb enabwed in youw config then /dev/fb0 wiww be cweated by vesafb
	and this dwivew wiww use fb1, fb2. In that case, you need to configuwe youw X-sewvew
	to use fb1. Anothew simpwe awthewnative is to disabwe vesafb fwom youw config.
